### Listar productos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products
Accept: application/json

### Crear producto
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teclado",
  "price": 19999,
  "currency": "ARS"
}

### Obtener un producto
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/prod_6d4640d7
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar parcialmente
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/products/prod_6d4640d7
Content-Type: application/json

{ "price": 21999 }

### Eliminar
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/products/prod_demo

### Productos por categoría
GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories/cat_peripherals/products?page=1&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Categorías
GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories
Accept: application/json

GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories/cat_peripherals
Accept: application/json

### Tags
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tags
Accept: application/json

GET http://localhost:3000/api/tags/tag_gaming
Accept: application/json

### Tags de un producto
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/prod_demo/tags
Accept: application/json

POST http://localhost:3000/api/products/prod_demo/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{ "tagId": "tag_gaming" }

DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/products/prod_demo/tags/tag_gaming

### Paginación offset
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?page=2&limit=10&sort=price,-createdAt
Accept: application/json

### Filtrado básico
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?status=active&categoryId=cat_peripherals
Accept: application/json

